<br>
She turned to swim quickly away, but there was a sudden sharp pain in her tail. &quot;Ahhhh... this one won't be going anywhere now.&quot; Holding the small seahorse close in an attempt to protect it, she struggled to move down the hallway, but it was no use. They were already upon her.<br>
<br>
It wasn't as bad an end as she thought it would be. Hopefully in their frenzy, they would miss the small seahorse. It gave her some small comfort as the world started to fade to darkness.<br>
<br>
&quot;Her hair... give me her hair!&quot;<br>
<br>
She would have gladly given them a lock of her hair if they had simply asked. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ukimayasilverbark.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kimaya Silverbark</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://prod.bsis.bellsouth.net/coDataImages/p/Groups/15/15568/folders/6507/67125button-wolf-pawprint" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tao Te Bark</span><br>  Posts: 440<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/22/02 7:00:30 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=427.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> (quick aside... the Kerra Isle snapshot reminded me of another... <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showMessage?topicID=297.topic">pub94.ezboard.com/ffirion...=297.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> ~ May Shiden now enjoy a happier place, with peace, quiet, and plenty of frosting )</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uenedlithien.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Enedlithien</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.shadow-striders.com/images/wolfIcon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 29<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/23/02 1:14:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=427.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.cpinternet.com/~theduke/MythStuff/ez-tres.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...prey thoughts</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> A harsh elven voice cried<hr>